cas-arch-requirement:2-2-2-2_Available-Power dc:description "The Mars Rover shall be operable for 4h under all of the following conditions:* The energy storage is fully loaded at the beginning* The operation requires less than or equal to 60% of the max energy in peak load* the environmental conditions are mission normal";
                                             dc:identifier "_17_0_3_1_60c0217_1554373992768_101922_18958";
                                             dc:title "Available Power";
                                             cas-arch:Requirement_partOf_Requirement cas-arch-requirement:2-2-2_Internal-Power-Supply;
