                                                 rdfs:label "2.2.2 Internal Power Supply".
cas-arch-requirement:2-2-3_Energy-Re-Charging dc:description "The Mars Rover shall re-charge the energy storage from 10% to 80% in 4h under the following conditions:* re-charging at mission normal conditions* no energy consumption of the Mars Rover since the re-charging period";
