                                              rdfs:label "2.2.3 Energy Re-Charging".
cas-arch-requirement:2-2-4_Energy-Management dc:description "The Mars Rover shall have an energy management fullfilling all of the following conditions:* distributing the energy to all systems* prioritizing the energy available for the different systems* limiting energy to individual systems to prioritize individual systems* managing energy that the Mars Rover can recharge by itself in a time period of less than 24 hours";
                                             dc:identifier "_17_0_3_1_60c0217_1554373886850_551019_15911";
                                             dc:title "Energy Management";
