cas-arch-requirement:2-7_Mars-Rover-Capabilities dc:description "The Mars Rover shall be able to execute the following operations individually and not in combination:* Moving on Mars surface* Capturing optical information* Capturing video information* Capturing audio information* Sampling of Probes of solid material of individual diameter not bigger than 20 mm* Sampling of probes of fluid material in the range of ph-value 0 to 11* Sampling of probes of gas of not more than 50 mm³ volume and pressure between 1 hPa up to 3.000 hPa* Sampling of biological probes of not more than 50 mm³ volume and not more than 30 mm length in any direction";
                                                 dc:identifier "_2021x_2_8d501e7_1710152920321_382759_5749";
                                                 dc:title "Mars Rover Capabilities";
