cas-arch-requirement:2-8-2_Landing-Deceleration dc:description "The Mars Rover shall be able to withstand landing deceleration as listed below:* Deceleration from 20.000 km/h at Mars atmosphere entry to 1.500 km/h in 4 minutes.* Deceleration from 1.500 km/s to 25 m/s in 3 minutes";
                                                dc:identifier "_2021x_2_8d501e7_1710150561344_954069_5661";
                                                dc:title "Landing Deceleration";
